  "reference_number": "IRN0263",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that Mehdi RASAKHI is an involved person under The Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: RASAKHI is or has been responsible for, engaging in or providing support for a serious human rights violation or abuse in Iran through his position as a judge at the Revolutionary Court of Rasht.\n",
